HEADWORD: Grassy
<hw>Grass"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Covered
with grass; abounding with grass; <as>as, a grassy lawn</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Resembling grass; green.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

